## IV. THE EIGHT ENGINEERING PILLARS

The IISL is not a theoretical abstraction. Each of its variables is addressable through specific, active 2025–2026 research programs. We organize these into eight engineering pillars that together constitute the full research agenda for Carbon-First Intelligence. Pillars 1–6 address B (structural integration) and E (energy efficiency). Pillar 4 addresses C (coherence) directly. Pillars 7 and 8 are new additions in Version 5.0, addressing dimensions of biological integration previously unformalized in this framework.

