**Parameter 5 — Optimized Mitochondrial Efficiency.** PGC-1α enhancement improves ATP production per glucose molecule and reduces ROS. Measured by metabolic efficiency (ATP per O₂ consumed), cognitive performance under metabolic load, and ROS biomarkers.

